videos.headline: Smith-Marsette takes off to score 45-yard Iowa TD
videos.description: Iowa's Ihmir Smith-Marsette gets the handoff and speeds down the sideline to score a 45-yard Iowa touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Smith-Marsette takes off to score 45-yard Iowa TD) 2019/11/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Iowa's Goodson races 55 yards to score TD
videos.description: Iowa takes a 14-3 lead over Nebraska as Tyler Goodson takes the handoff and navigates his way 55 yards downfield to score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Iowa's Goodson races 55 yards to score TD) 2019/11/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Iowa's Stanley throws pick-6 in the 2nd quarter
videos.description: Nate Stanley has his pass tipped and picked off by Cam Taylor-Britt, who takes it to the house for a 38-yard pick-6.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Iowa's Stanley throws pick-6 in the 2nd quarter) 2019/11/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Iowa answers pick-6 with 95-yard kickoff-return TD
videos.description: Ihmir Smith-Marsette answers Nebraska's pick-6 with an immediate 95-yard kickoff return to the house, giving Iowa a 24-10 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Iowa answers pick-6 with 95-yard kickoff-return TD) 2019/11/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: McCaffrey connects with Spielman for 39-yard Nebraska TD
videos.description: Luke McCaffrey rolls out and finds JD Spielman streaking to the end zone to score a 39-yard Nebraska touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (McCaffrey connects with Spielman for 39-yard Nebraska TD) 2019/11/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Mazour scores nine-yard Nebraska TD
videos.description: Nebraska's Wyatt Mazour takes the handoff and battles his way nine yards to score a touchdown and tie the game at 24-24.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Mazour scores nine-yard Nebraska TD) 2019/11/29 ESHEET
